        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "refactor(skills): trim bundled starter set",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- reduce the core-bundled starter set from 57 skill directories to 14:\n  `clawhub`, `diagram-maker`, `gifgrep`, `gog`, `healthcheck`, `mcporter`,\n  `model-usage`, `node-connect`, `peekaboo`, `skill-creator`, `songsee`,\n  `spotify-player`, `summarize`, and `weather`\n- move five owner-specific skills into their plugins and declare the plugin\n  skill surfaces: Canvas, Discord, Slack, voice-call, and WhatsApp (`wacli`)\n- remove 38 optional skills from core, clean up the retained ClawHub skill to\n  use native `openclaw skills` discovery/install commands, and update affected\n  docs, generated plugin inventory, and obsolete tests\n\nPlugin-owned skills are now visible when their owning plugin is active. This is\nintentional for `wacli` as well as the channel/capability skills. The root\n`skills/` directory and bundled-skill loading/configuration remain in place.\nThere are no system-prompt changes.\n\nRemoved from core:\n\n`1password`, `apple-notes`, `apple-reminders`, `bear-notes`, `blogwatcher`,\n`blucli`, `camsnap`, `coding-agent`, `eightctl`, `gemini`, `gh-issues`,\n`github`, `goplaces`, `himalaya`, `imsg`, `meme-maker`, `nano-pdf`,\n`node-inspect-debugger`, `notion`, `obsidian`, `openai-whisper`,\n`openai-whisper-api`, `openhue`, `oracle`, `ordercli`, `python-debugpy`, `sag`,\n`session-logs`, `sherpa-onnx-tts`, `sonoscli`, `spike`, `taskflow`,\n`taskflow-inbox-triage`, `things-mac`, `tmux`, `trello`, `video-frames`, and\n`xurl`.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/skills/discovery/status-workspace.test.ts src/skills/loading/env-path-guidance.test.ts src/skills/loading/plugin-skills.test.ts src/skills/loading/workspace-load.test.ts src/plugins/copy-bundled-plugin-metadata.test.ts src/plugins/stage-bundled-plugin-runtime.test.ts test/plugin-npm-package-manifest.test.ts src/cli/skills-cli.commands.test.ts`\n  - 160 tests passed across 4 Vitest shards after the final rebase\n- `pnpm plugins:inventory:check`\n- changed-file `oxfmt --check`\n- AWS Crabbox `cbx_661e89a92661`: `pnpm check:changed` passed\n- AWS Crabbox `cbx_37e3ec8f7902`: `pnpm build` passed\n- autoreview: no accepted/actionable findings; rejected the standalone `wacli`\n  visibility finding because moving it under the WhatsApp plugin is the\n  intentional owner-boundary change\n",
